Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.00,0:23:59.47,Behind the Scenes,,0000,0000,0000,,Professor Moriarty,\Nwho loves lobster...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.64,0:24:03.63,Behind the Scenes,,0000,0000,0000,,stole the most expensive lobster in\Nthe world form Brydon mansion.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.11,0:24:06.58,Behind the Scenes,,0000,0000,0000,,This lobster is made of\Njewels and coral.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.65,0:24:08.77,Behind the Scenes,,0000,0000,0000,,It was put into a barrel and\Nshipped from the harbour.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.98,0:24:12.01,Behind the Scenes,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of taste does\Nthis lobster have?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.75,0:24:16.81,Behind the Scenes,,0000,0000,0000,,If you find yourself in a mystery,\Nplease come see us at Baker Street.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.13,0:24:22.03,Ep Title,,0000,0000,0000,,Gourmet! Coral Lobsters.
